28/08/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- President Alfred Moisiu called on diplomats Wednesday (27 August) to promote Albania's image abroad. Speaking at the annual meeting of Albanian ambassadors, he said relations with Western countries should be strengthened. He also called for the establishment of a ministry of emigration that would serve the needs of Albanian expatriates. He noted that 25 per cent of all Albanians live abroad. (ATA, Albanian Daily News - 27/08/03)
